OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772565071
OL,3,CKSI buys stake in Dagenham & Redbridge
OL,4,Cand plans to take club to Premier
OL,5,CLeague
OL,7,FYouTuber KSI says he wants to do the
OL,8,F"unthinkable" and take Dagenham and
OL,9,FRedbridge FC to the Premier League
OL,10,Fafter becoming one of the club's
OL,11,Fowners.
OL,13,FThe east London side was relegated at
OL,14,Fthe end of the 2024-25 season and
OL,15,Fdropped down to the sixth tier,
OL,16,FNational League South after failing to
OL,17,Fget enough points.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
