PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772565071
OL,3,CKSI buys stake in Dagenham & Redbridge
OL,4,Cand plans to take club to Premier
OL,5,CLeague
OL,7,FKSI said being an owner of Dagenham
OL,8,Fand Redbridge felt "surreal", and he
OL,9,Fwanted to bring back the excitment and
OL,10,Fhappiness.
OL,12,FHe added: "I want the place to be
OL,13,Frocking. I want it to be an event.
OL,15,F"With this club, I want to do the
OL,16,Funthinkable. I want to take Dagenham
OL,17,Fand Redbridge to the Premier League.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
