FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772565071
OL,3,CKSI buys stake in Dagenham & Redbridge
OL,4,Cand plans to take club to Premier
OL,5,CLeague
OL,7,F"It's obviously going to take time. We
OL,8,Fneed to improve the team, have some
OL,9,Fadditions to really take it to another
OL,10,Flevel.
OL,12,F"And I want to build the community.
OL,13,FEveryone here is fantastic, hard
OL,14,Fworking people, and I want to be the
OL,15,Fman that can affect things on the
OL,16,Fpitch as well as off the pitch.
OL,18,F"You guys have been here way longer
OL,19,Fthan I have and I know to some of you
OL,20,Fit might be scary, me being one of the
OL,21,Fowners, but I'm reachable.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772565071
OL,3,CKSI buys stake in Dagenham & Redbridge
OL,4,Cand plans to take club to Premier
OL,5,CLeague
OL,7,F"You can literally tweet me and I will
OL,8,Fsee it. You can let your frustrations
OL,9,Fout to me or celebrate with me.
OL,11,F"I'm approachable.
OL,13,F"I'm a fighter. I've broken my nose,
OL,14,FI've broken my hand, I've broken my
OL,15,Fthumb. I've been in tough fights, but
OL,16,FI keep going no matter what.
OL,18,F"With Daggers, I'm gonna keep
OL,19,Ffighting. I'm gonna do everything I
OL,20,Fcan to make sure we succeed. I'm just
OL,21,Fready to get started."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
